go-yaml-yq
==========

This repository contains code copied from github.com/mikefarah/yq in
internal/yqlib/.

Source: https://github.com/mikefarah/yq
Commit: 8e2c9b612d3dabc6fe1390dfdca2af49bf4c6e66
License: MIT

The copied yq code has been pruned by deleting whole format-adapter files and
making the corresponding no_* stubs unconditional. It is otherwise intended to
remain mechanically comparable with upstream yq's pkg/yqlib package.

